SaavnDriver - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnDriver class is the main class of the program which initiates the map reduce job.
SaavnStreamingKey - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnStreamingKey class is used as the Output Key class for the Mapper class SaavnStreamingMapper .
SaavnStreamingKey(IntWritable, Text) - Constructor for class com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce.SaavnStreamingKey
The constructor constructs an object of type SaavnStreamingKey by setting values for trendingDay and songId .
SaavnStreamingMapper - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnStreamingMapper class is an implementation of the Mapper class which is used to filter the Saavn streaming data before it is sent to the partitioner class SaavnStreamingPartitioner .
SaavnStreamingPartitioner - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnStreamingPartitioner class is used to partition the map output on trendingDay before sending the partitioned output to the reducer class SaavnStreamingReducer .
SaavnStreamingReducer - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnStreamingReducer class is an implementation of the Reducer class which is used to aggregate the map output which is partitioned based on trendingDay .
SaavnStreamingValue - Class in com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce
The SaavnStreamingValue class is used as the Output Value class for the Mapper class SaavnStreamingMapper .
SaavnStreamingValue(int, int) - Constructor for class com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce.SaavnStreamingValue
The constructor constructs an object of type SaavnStreamingValue by setting values for trendingDay and songWeight .
setConf(Configuration) - Method in class com.upgrad.pgpbde.project.map.reduce.SaavnStreamingPartitioner
Each trendingDay is mapped to a unique reducer number for the map output to be partitioned accordingly.
